    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262160/extras/001aad729671f3c787b9b48e83333acf.avif?t=1771124831\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262160/extras_big/001aad729671f3c787b9b48e83333acf.avif?t=1771124831 width=800 height=266 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on an epic journey in this Roguelite to reclaim Asgard in a world left desolate after Ragnarok. With all the old gods dead, the realms have descended into chaos, overrun by malevolent creatures and remnants of shattered divine power. As the last surviving descendant of Baldr, you must traverse the dangerous and ever-changing landscapes of Helheim, Muspelheim, and other legendary realms, battling fearsome enemies and uncovering forgotten secrets. Each run offers new challenges, powerful relics, and the chance to restore what was lost, with the ultimate goal of reclaiming Asgard and rebuilding a world torn apart by the end of the gods.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262160/extras/a4b4b2f6490772b475c97c770e076eca.avif?t=1771124831\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262160/extras_big/a4b4b2f6490772b475c97c770e076eca.avif?t=1771124831 width=800 height=267 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore and choose a new path each run</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Unlock abilities and Items and upgrades </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Befriend or cross characters throughout your journey </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Encounter a wide variety of enemies in the Norse realms</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Challenging bosses and puzzles </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Roguelite </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262160/extras/836ff12e94902b68f13389172de416a0.poster.avif?t=1771124831\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262160/extras/836ff12e94902b68f13389172de416a0.webm?t=1771124831\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262160/extras/836ff12e94902b68f13389172de416a0.mp4?t=1771124831\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
